##INTRODUCTION

In this program we are going to print star pattern by taking numbers from users, means it will print star pattern by users choice.


##EXAMPLE

Let's say we want 6 rows of stars
then, output will be,
*
**
***
****
*****
******


##PROGRAM

#include <stdio.h>
void starPattern(int rows)
{
    for(int i = 0; i < rows; i++)
    {
        for(int j = 0; j <= i; j++)
        {
            printf("*");
        }
        printf("\n");
    }
}

int main()
{
    int rows;
    printf("How many rows do you want?\n");
    scanf("%d", &rows);
    starPattern(rows);
    return 0;
}
